step1：
  download Nexus Repository OSS 3.2.1-01 from 
    https://sonatype-download.global.ssl.fastly.net/nexus/3/nexus-3.2.1-01-unix.tar.gz

step2：
    tar -zxvf nexus-3.2.1-01-unix.tar.gz
    
step3:
  cd /home/devel/software/nexus/nexus-3.2.1-01/bin
  sudo ./nexus run
  ./nexus run
  if the step succeed,it will appear the command：Started Sonatype Nexus OSS 3.2.1-01
  

    
